Q">Nam Việt hành - 南越行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Chu-Chi-T%C3%A0i/author-9i8XaM0gzFC7E9e0G52Oug">Chu Chi Tài</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-26sSUlnxwSbNqm1W_qw_nw">Tái hạ khúc kỳ 1 - 塞下曲其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/T%C3%A1i-h%E1%BA%A1-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-ONXOnvmlG2uX7LAXqg-gUA">Tái hạ khúc kỳ 3 - 塞下曲其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-T%E1%BB%91/author-RmmfVoamdwhG77VOgdRDUQ">Trương Trọng Tố</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%A0o/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-10/poem-m3I9sIsmieBsZFQACM3Q3Q">Thuỷ điệu từ kỳ 10 - 水調詞其十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%A0o/author--abLwbhK7CuzmdoZ83_cZw">Trần Đào</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Ph%E1%BB%A5/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-II/poem-2-idPPU0oU7ORO8kaZA0Fw">Vương Chiêu Quân (II) - 王昭君 (II)</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Ph%E1%BB%A5/author-oBydTx_0LTm0Yp4yKfhzOg">Thôi Quốc Phụ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
